data.description: Perched atop the picturesque Makakilo Kahiwelo neighborhood, this enchanting residence beckons with a blend of comfort and versatility. The well-appointed kitchen, adorned with Corian Countertops and new Stainless Steel appliances, invites culinary delights. A breakfast bar and formal dining area cater to both casual and elegant dining experiences.    Embrace sustainable living with 26 photovoltaic panels, promising not only environmental consciousness but also utility savings. Central AC ensures evenings are cool and comfortable, while the freshly painted interior adds a touch of modern allure. Outside, a beautiful retaining wall and custom steel gates frame a lovely yard, creating a perfect play space for the kids.    As the day unfolds, savor breathtaking sunsets and ocean views, transforming this haven into a peaceful retreat. Welcome to a home where luxury and practicality harmonize, offering a lifestyle that celebrates both the environment and the joy of family living.
